-- Endurance Names Kuhn Chief Executive Officer of Global Insurance
-- B y   S u s a n n a   P a k
-- 2012-11-19T13:41:10Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-11-19/endurance-names-kuhn-chief-executive-officer-of-global-insurance.html
Endurance Specialty Holdings Ltd.,
the Bermuda-based insurer, has hired John Kuhn as chief
executive officer of global insurance.  Kuhn, who most recently worked as the chief underwriting
officer at Axis Capital Holdings Ltd., will be joining next
week, Endurance said today in a statement.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Susanna Pak in  New York  at 
